title: For Sale:  2 Gun Survival Set H&R Topper 12ga & Taurus Judge
location: West virginia, West Virginia, United States
postcontent: This is the ultimate survival package. Using just one properly equipped long gun and one handgun the owner of this package can ACCURATELY shoot 12 different cartridges in the long gun and 6 cartridges in the handgun. That’s a total of 15 different cartridges using one long gun and one handgun: 12 ga, 20 ga, 410 bore, 22 Short, 22 Long, 22 Long Rifle, 380 ACP, 9mm Luger, 357 Magnum, 38 Special, 40 S&W, 44 Magnum, 44 Special, 45 ACP, and 45 Colt. This auction includes: H&R 12ga shotgun with beautiful case hardened receiver, factory ventilated recoil pad, 24" cylinder bore barrel, factory iron sights, screw-in chokes, hammer extension, swivel studs, and nylon sling. Complete NIB (unfired) 8-piece set of Chiappa 8” rifled adapters for the shotgun. Also included is a Taurus Judge revolver 2.5” chamber, 3” barrel, matte stainless. Box & paperwork included. Four Short Lane smooth bore adapters for the Taurus Judge in 22 Short, 22 Long, and 22 Long Rifle, 380 ACP, 38 Special, and 9mm Luger. In a survival situation the ability to use whatever ammunition is available may be important.  The H&R 12 ga shotgun came from the factory with a 24" cylinder bore barrel and iron sights. I assume that these guns were produced with iron sights to shoot rifled (Foster) slugs and this gun does that well. It also shoots sabot slugs accurately using a rifled choke tube (not included in this sale). I have extensive experience in using gauge adapters. I can say from personal experience that shooting pistol cartridges in a shotgun with a plain bead front sight is an exercise in futility. Having real iron sights like the factory rifle sights on this gun makes a huge difference when shooting pistol cartridges in a long gun. With this set, in addition to having the ability to use many different pistol calibers and shotgun gauges you will have the option to choose your choke using screw-in Browning Invector choke tubes. I had the barrel threaded for screw-in choke tubes by R&D Custom Barrel Service. This makes reasonable patterns possible whether you are shooting 12 ga, 20 ga, or 410 bore shells in this 12 ga shotgun. This sale includes seven Browning Invector choke tubes in a MTM Case Guard case. Choke tubes included: cylinder, skeet, improved cylinder, modified, improved modified, full, and an extended knurled extra full/tukey tube. All in all these are pretty versatile guns. I will not separate the components of this set. Everything goes as a single package: one long gun, one handgun, 12ea gauge adapters, and 7ea choke tubes.
